== Doing everything from the commandline

* Many people use git
+* Many of those use it from the commandline
+* Many of those use github
+* Many of those switch to the browser for viewing issues, creating
  or merging pull requests
+* That's not necessary =)
  There's https://github.com/ingydotnet/git-hub
+* Written in, er, bash

