== Creating repos

* git hub repo-init, repo-new
+* git hub repo-init mycoolstuff:
+ * Creates directory
+ * Creates repo on github
+ * Clones repo
+ * media/repo-init.ogv

----
== Handling Pull Requests

* git hub pr-list, pr-diff, pr-fetch
+* git hub pr-list [user/repo]: List pull requests for current repo
+* git hub pr-diff [user/repo] num: Show diff for pull request
+* git hub pr-fetch [user/repo] num: Fetch pull request into a local branch PR/num
+* git hub issue-resolve [user/repo] num:
  Write a comment and close issue
+* media/pr-fetch.ogv

----
== Commenting issues

* git hub comment [user/repo] num: Write a comment
